target: You are very welcome. Enjoy your time in Cambridge.
context: <user>  What Chinese restaurants are there in the center of town? <system>  There are 10 Chinese restaurants in the centre of town. Would you like a moderately priced one or an expensive one? We have a few cheap. <user>  I'd like an expensive one please. <system>  I have found tang Chinese which is here in the centre. Would you like to start a reservation? <user>  Yes, please book a table for 4 people at 16:15 on Friday and send me the reference number once it is booked. <system>  I've made your reservation at Tang Chinese for 4 at 16:15, reference #D6G7VSV0 . Will that be all? <user>  Actually I'd also like suggestions on areas to visit at the center of town <system>  There's a church called all saints church you could visit, it's listed under architecture.<user>  Can I get the address and entrance fee. <system>  The address is Jesus Lane, and there is no entrance fee. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?<user>  Yes. Can you help me book a taxi so I can get to the restaurant on time. <system>  Yes, I reserved a Red Tesla for you. The contact number is 07612290033. Is there anything else I can help with?<user>  Will the Red Tesla get me to the restaurant for my 16:15 reservation? <system>  Yes, your taxi will pick you up at all saints church and arrive at tang chinese by 16:15. Is there anything else I can do for you today?<user>  Ok sounds great. That's all I need. Thank You! <system>
